scenarioText: The customer recently downloaded the Westpac banking app and is trying to transfer funds to a friend but cannot figure out how to do it. They are unsure where to find the transfer option in the app and are worried they might accidentally send money to the wrong person. They want clear, step-by-step instructions on how to transfer funds securely and are also curious if there are any daily transfer limits they should be aware of.
